import React from "react";
import CenteredLayout from "../common/centeredLayout";
import { Button, Checkbox, Form, Select, Input, TextArea, Image } from "semantic-ui-react";

const genderOptions =[
  {key: "m", text: "male", value:"male"},
  {key: "j", text: "female", value:"female"},
  {key: "k", text: "kale", value: "kale"},
  {key: "o", text: "other", value:"other"},
]

const registerRestaurant = () => (
  <CenteredLayout>
  <Form>
    <Form.Field
      control={Input} label="Nombre del Restaurante"
      maxLength="50" placeholder='Nombre del Restaurante'
    />
    <Form.Group widths='equal'>
    <Form.Field
      control={Input} label="Dirección del Restaurante"
      maxLength="50" placeholder='DirecciÓn del Restaurante'
    />
    <Form.Field
        control={Select}
        options={genderOptions}
        label={{ children: 'Provincia', htmlFor: 'form-select-control-gender' }}
        placeholder='Provincia'
        search
        searchInput={{ id: 'form-select-control-gender' }}
    />
    </Form.Group>
    <Form.Group widths='equal'>
    <Form.Field
          control={TextArea} label='Información adicional del restaurante'
          maxLength="50" placeholder='Tell us more about you...'
    />
    <Form.Field
      control={Input} label="Correo Electrónico"
      maxLength="50" placeholder='Correo Electrónico'
    />
    </Form.Group>
    <Form.Group widths='equal'>
    <Form.Field
      control={Input} label="Dirección de su sitio web"
      maxLength="50" placeholder='Dirección de su sitio web'
    />
    <Form.Field
      control={Input} label="Teléfono"
      maxLength="50" placeholder='Teléfono'
    />
    </Form.Group>
    <Form.Group widths='equal'>
    <Form.Field
      control={Input} label="Dirección página de publicidad"
      maxLength="50" placeholder='Dirección página de publicidad'
    />
    <Form.Field
      control={Input} label="Categoría del Restaurante"
      maxLength="50" placeholder='Categoría del Restaurante'
    />
    </Form.Group>
    <Form.Group widths='equal'>
    <Form.Field
    control={Image} label="Fotografía del logo del Restaurante"
    control={Button} name="Guardar"
    Image src='https://react.semantic-ui.com/images/wireframe/square-image.png' 
    size='small' circular
    />
    <Form.Field
      control={TextArea} label="Descripción del Restaurante"
      maxLength="50" placeholder='Descripción del Restaurante'
    />
    </Form.Group>
    <Form.Group widths='equal'>
       <Form.Field control={Button}>Cancelar</Form.Field>
       <Form.Field control={Button}>Guardar</Form.Field>
    </Form.Group>
  </Form>
  </CenteredLayout>
)

export default registerRestaurant;
